folder: Auburn Place & Elliot Place (North), Brooklyn, NY
text:
Auburn Place, north side, between North Elliot Place and North Portland Avenue, showing the New Cumberland Hospital. The views are from Myrtle Avenue across the clearance where Fort Green Houses will be erected.

April 22, 1941
Views 1,2,3

P.L. Sperr
